    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
      <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Aink423-kilavi">kārpparuvattē piriyak karutiya talaimakaṟkut tōḻi talaimakaḷatu āṟṟāmai kūṟic celavaḻuṅkuvittatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">The confidante told [this] to the hero, who had considered leaving during the rainy season, and stopped the journey.</p>
            </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <lg xml:id="Aink423">        
<l>māmaḻai yiṭiyūut taḷicorin taṉṟē</l>
<l>vāṇutal pacappac celavayarn taṉaiyē</l>
<l>yāmē niṟṟuṟan tamaiyala</l>
<l>māymala ruṇkaṇu nīrniṟain taṉavē.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg xml:lang="en">
            <l>The dark clouds thundered and poured down raindrops.</l>
            <l>You have decided on going so that [her] bright forehead became pale.</l> 
            <l>We are not content to let go of you.</l>
            <l>[Her] kajal eyes like beautiful blossoms well up with water.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </body>
    </text>
